HEADWORD: focussing
<hw>focussing</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>the concentration of attention or energy on
something.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> focus, focussing.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>the act of bringing into focus.</def>⟦br⟧
